        "**Step 4:** $~$ Apply Boundary Condition\n",
        "\n",
        "At $r = 1$, the boundary condition is:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$u(1, \\phi) = \\sum_{\\ell=0}^\\infty A_\\ell P_\\ell(\\cos\\phi) = 1 + \\cos\\phi$$\n",
        "\n",
        "We expand $1 + \\cos\\phi$ in terms of Legendre polynomials\n",
