        "So this corresponds to:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$A_0 = 1, \\quad A_2 = 1, \\quad A_\\ell = 0 \\text{ for } \\ell \\ne 0,2$$\n",
        "\n",
        "**Final Solution**\n",
        "\n",
        "$$u(r, \\phi) = \\frac{1}{r} P_0(\\cos\\phi) + \\frac{1}{r^3} P_2(\\cos\\phi)\n",
        "= \\frac{1}{r} + \\frac{1}{r^3} \\cos 2\\phi$$\n",
